    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hey! It's here to expose a feature of the RefinementList (component) to the widget.\n\nSo that if you want to build a list of checkboxes where only one checkbox can be ticked at a time, while still displaying the other options then you use refinementList + singleRefine, then you can.\n\nLike \"shipping options\" (point relais, collissimo..) it fits in it, while using a menu for shipping options may not be obvious to the user.\n\nWhat do you think?\n",
