    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> So that if you want to build a list of checkboxes where only one checkbox can be ticked at a time, while still displaying the other options then you use refinementList + singleRefine, then you can.\n\nBut isn't exactly what the menu is doing? Having a list where only one item can be checked at a time ? \n\nIn the end I think we need to remove `refinementList` from the exposed widgets. Instead we should expose widgets for each use-case. Maybe we should keep this discussion in #219?\n",
