    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Back from the other discussion, here are my current thoughts:\n- We keep the `refinementList` as a widget (me suggesting removing it was a misunderstanding on my part)\n- We remove the `singleRefine` option form the `refinementList` widget (we keep it in the component). We already have the `menu` widget for that. Maybe this is not the best name, but we can work on finding a better name on another issue (`singleSelection`, `radioList`, ...)\n",
